voidable given `record_count` is a session total. P2 document.\n\n## Summary\n- **P1 easy fix now:** redaction full-string re-lowercase per match (redaction.rs:191) → in-place `replace_range` on `lower`.\n- **P1 document as POC tradeoff:** skim reads each session's turn-details and full transcript ~2× (find_related + timeline); turn summaries parsed 3×/session; `show` transcript scan unbounded in pathological hash ordering.\n- **P2 document:** per-call transcript sort in `session_previews`; Value/String clones in hydration loops.\n\nNo files edited."}],"totalDurationMs":39579,"totalTokens":60381,"totalToolUseCount":8,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":40662,"cache_read_input_tokens":17670,"output_tokens":2047,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":40662},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":2,"output_tokens":2047,"cache_read_input_tokens":17670,"cache_creation_input_tokens":40662,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":40662,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"toolStats":{"readCount":8,"searchCount":0,"bashCount":0,"editFileCount":0,"linesAdded":0,"linesRemoved":0,"otherToolCount":0}},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"[REDACTED:entropy]","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-desktop","cwd":"[REDACTED:entropy]","sessionId":"[REDACTED:entropy]","version":"2.1.142","gitBranch":"[REDACTED:entropy]"}}